               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380820-name-352" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-352" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-352" type="surname" value="BIRCH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-352" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH BIRCH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a butcher, and live at Islington. On the 6th of July, a fore-quarter of mutton was hanging outside my shop, as butchers Usually hang their meat—there was about 19lbs.—I missed it at half-past ten o'clock at night—I saw it again the next morning—I knew it was mine—I have seen the prisoner before.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183808200052"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380820-name-353" type="witnessName">
