                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-353" type="surname" value="M'DONALD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-353" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>ANN M'DONALD</persName>
                  </hi>. I live near Mr. Birch's shop—I saw the prisoner carrying some mutton under his arm, about half-past ten o'clock at night on the 6th of July.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380820-name-354" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-354" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-354" type="surname" value="M'DONALD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-354" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT M'DONALD</persName>
                  </hi>. I saw the prisoner carrying a fore-quarter of mutton on his shoulder about half-past ten o'clock, on Friday night, on the 6th of July, he was fifty yards from the prosecutor's shop—I had known him before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380820-name-355" type="witnessName">
