                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-355" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM CHING</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I took the prisoner—I found the mutton in a house in Windsor-street, where he resides—I took the prisoner in the street.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I kicked against it, and took it up-went to a house in Duddy's-rents, and put it under the tiles, on the roof of the house.</p>
